@page "/About"

<PageTitle>About TagzApp</PageTitle>

<div class="container">
    <h1 class="mb-4">About TagzApp</h1>
    
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <section class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="h3 mb-3">What is TagzApp?</h2>
                <p class="lead">
                    TagzApp is a modern, real-time social media aggregation platform that brings together content from multiple social networks into a single, unified view. 
                    Built with cutting-edge .NET technologies, TagzApp allows you to monitor hashtags, track conversations, and engage with your audience across various platforms simultaneously.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Whether you're running a conference, managing a brand, or simply want to keep track of trending topics, TagzApp provides a powerful and flexible solution 
                    for social media monitoring and engagement.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="h3 mb-3">Connected Social Media Networks</h2>
                <p>TagzApp currently integrates with the following social media platforms:</p>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-twitter text-primary me-2"></i><strong>Twitter/X</strong> - Posts and hashtag monitoring</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-mastodon text-primary me-2"></i><strong>Mastodon</strong> - Decentralized social networking</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-twitch text-primary me-2"></i><strong>Twitch Chat</strong> - Live streaming chat integration</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-youtube text-primary me-2"></i><strong>YouTube</strong> - Video content and comments</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-youtube text-primary me-2"></i><strong>YouTube Chat</strong> - Live stream chat monitoring</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-cloud text-primary me-2"></i><strong>Bluesky</strong> - AT Protocol social network</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-rss text-primary me-2"></i><strong>Blazot</strong> - Custom content feeds</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-up text-primary me-2"></i><strong>Azure Queue</strong> - Message queuing system</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="alert alert-info">
                    <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>
                    <strong>Note:</strong> All content displayed in TagzApp comes from public posts and messages that are already available on these platforms. 
                    We respect each platform's privacy settings and terms of service.
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-5">
                <h2 class="h3 mb-3">Technology Stack</h2>
                <p>TagzApp is built using modern Microsoft technologies and open-source frameworks:</p>
                
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h4 class="h5">Core Technologies</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>.NET 9.0</strong> - Latest .NET platform</li>
                            <li><strong>ASP.NET Core Blazor</strong> - Interactive web UI framework</li>
                            <li><strong>Blazor WebAssembly</strong> - Client-side execution</li>
                            <li><strong>SignalR</strong> - Real-time web functionality</li>
                            <li><strong>.NET Aspire</strong> - Cloud-native application development</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h4 class="h5">Frontend Libraries</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Bootstrap 5</strong> - Responsive CSS framework</li>
                            <li><strong>Bootstrap Icons</strong> - Comprehensive icon library</li>
                            <li><strong>jQuery</strong> - JavaScript utility library</li>
                            <li><strong>Markdown Editor</strong> - Rich text editing</li>
                            <li><strong>SweetAlert</strong> - Beautiful alert dialogs</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row mt-3">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h4 class="h5">Data & Storage</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Entity Framework Core</strong> - Object-relational mapping</li>
                            <li><strong>PostgreSQL</strong> - Production database</li>
                            <li><strong>SQLite</strong> - Development database</li>
                            <li><strong>Azure Storage Queues</strong> - Message processing</li>
                            <li><strong>Redis</strong> - Caching and session storage</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h4 class="h5">Authentication & Security</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>ASP.NET Core Identity</strong> - User management</li>
                            <li><strong>OAuth 2.0</strong> - Third-party authentication</li>
                            <li><strong>GitHub Authentication</strong> - Developer sign-in</li>
                            <li><strong>Google Authentication</strong> - Social login</li>
                            <li><strong>LinkedIn Authentication</strong> - Professional networks</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row mt-3">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h4 class="h5">Monitoring & Observability</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>OpenTelemetry</strong> - Distributed tracing</li>
                            <li><strong>Application Insights</strong> - Azure monitoring</li>
                            <li><strong>Structured Logging</strong> - Comprehensive diagnostics</li>
                            <li><strong>Health Checks</strong> - Service monitoring</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h4 class="h5">Development & Testing</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>xUnit</strong> - Unit testing framework</li>
                            <li><strong>Playwright</strong> - End-to-end testing</li>
                            <li><strong>Bogus</strong> - Test data generation</li>
                            <li><strong>Git Versioning</strong> - Automated versioning</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

